title: The Bear
body:
Brienne and Jaime talk over the campfire.

i’m no maiden fair, no, you would be the bear

Brienne lay before the campfire, her eyes starting to close after yet another long day of hauling her prisoner through the forest. When she had initially accepted the task she had expected it to be…
